data.meta_description: Andreas, 8th Prince of Leiningen, 3rd child and 2nd son of Emich Kyrill, 7th Prince of Leiningen. Andreas succeeded his father as Head of the Family due to his older brother Karl Emich's unequal 2nd marriage. Andreas married and has 3 children. Like his brother and 2 sisters, Andreas is a direct descendant of QV and both her siblings, half-brother Carl, 3rd Prince of Leiningen, and half-sister Princess Feodora of Hohenlohe-Langenburg, nee of Leiningen.
